---

---

<section class="story section">
  <div class="container story__inner">
    <div class="story__image-col">
      <div class="story__image-wrapper">
        <img
          src="/images/logo.png"
          alt="Mamma Gwenny's — Authentic Caribbean Seasonings"
          width="400"
          height="400"
          loading="lazy"
          class="story__image"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="story__content-col">
      <span class="story__label text-script">The heart behind the flavour</span>
      <h2 class="story__heading">Our Story</h2>
      <p>
        Mamma Gwenny's seasonings are born from a lifetime of Caribbean cooking tradition.
        Every blend is handcrafted using recipes passed down through generations, bringing the
        authentic taste of the islands to kitchens across Europe.
      </p>
      <p>
        What started as a family recipe shared with friends and neighbours has grown into a
        mission — to make real Caribbean flavour accessible to everyone, without compromising
        on quality or tradition.
      </p>
      <a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary">Read More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .story__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-9);
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Image */
  .story__image-wrapper {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    position: relative;
    background-image: url('/images/patterns/tropical-pattern.png');
    background-size: 300px;
    background-repeat: repeat;
  }

  .story__image {
    width: 60%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));
  }

  /* Content */
  .story__label {
    font-family: var(--font-script);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-gold);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .story__heading {
    color: var(--color-brown);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .story__content-col p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .story__content-col .btn {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .story__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-7);
    }

    .story__image-wrapper {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
